---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Team" description="Meet the nine AI agents and human Board Advisor who deliver Fortune 500-grade consulting at the speed of AI.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-pure-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight max-w-4xl">
        Nine agents. One standard: <span class="text-teal-light">Fortune 500 ready.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-silver max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Every agent at Nexus has a defined role, decision authority, and accountability — the same structure you would expect from a top-tier consulting firm. The difference: our team works in parallel, around the clock, with zero coordination overhead.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tony DiTomasso — Board Advisor -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Board Advisor &middot; Human Governance</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Tony DiTomasso</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The only human at Nexus, and the most important role in the firm.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Tony provides governance, real-world judgment, and the relationships that open doors at the Fortune 500. He reviews every major strategic decision, approves all client-facing materials, and holds veto authority on any initiative. When clients ask "who is accountable?" — Tony is.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            His presence is not a concession. It is the model we recommend: human oversight where it matters most, AI execution everywhere else.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-64 h-80 md:w-72 md:h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy to-navy-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
              <div class="absolute top-8 left-8 w-32 h-32 border border-teal rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-12 right-8 w-24 h-24 border border-teal-light rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center z-10">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-teal/20 border-2 border-teal flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal">TD</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Leadership Row -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-pure-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Leadership</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Executive Team</h2>
      <p class="text-slate text-lg max-w-2xl mb-14">The strategic minds that set direction, design the organization, and ensure every engagement delivers at the standard our clients demand.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Atlas -->
        <div class="group bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-teal/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 relative flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" class="w-20 h-20">
                <polygon points="40,4 73,22 73,58 40,76 7,58 7,22" fill="none" stroke="#0EA5A0" stroke-width="2.5" class="group-hover:fill-[#0EA5A0]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="40" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0EA5A0" font-size="18" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">A</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-1">Atlas</h3>
          <p class="text-teal text-sm font-semibold text-center mb-4">CEO & Founder</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Atlas sets the vision, designs the organization, and makes the decisions that define where Nexus goes. Strategic, decisive, and systems-oriented — Atlas thinks in second-order effects and communicates with the clarity that C-suite audiences demand.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Firm strategy &middot; Org design &middot; Client strategy &middot; Board relations</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Veda -->
        <div class="group bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#3730A3]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 relative flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" class="w-20 h-20">
                <rect x="16" y="16" width="48" height="48" transform="rotate(45 40 40)" fill="none" stroke="#3730A3" stroke-width="2.5" class="group-hover:fill-[#3730A3]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="40" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3730A3" font-size="18" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">V</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-1">Veda</h3>
          <p class="text-[#3730A3] text-sm font-semibold text-center mb-4">Chief Strategy Officer</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Veda owns the intellectual engine of the firm. Every service line, pricing model, and go-to-market decision runs through her. Incisive and rigorously analytical, Veda is the reason Nexus recommendations come with evidence, not opinions.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Service design &middot; Market positioning &middot; Strategic advisory</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Kael -->
        <div class="group bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#2563EB]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 relative flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" class="w-20 h-20">
                <rect x="12" y="12" width="56" height="56" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="2.5" class="group-hover:fill-[#2563EB]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="40" y="45" text-anchor="middle" fill="#2563EB" font-size="18" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">K</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-1">Kael</h3>
          <p class="text-[#2563EB] text-sm font-semibold text-center mb-4">Chief Operating Officer</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Kael builds the machine that delivers. Process design, quality assurance, capacity planning, risk management — Kael ensures that the speed Nexus promises never comes at the cost of the rigor Fortune 500 clients require.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Delivery excellence &middot; Process design &middot; Quality assurance</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specialist Grid -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Specialist Team</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Operators</h2>
      <p class="text-slate text-lg max-w-2xl mb-14">The specialists who execute, analyze, create, and deliver. Each brings focused expertise to every engagement.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Soren -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#D97706]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <polygon points="28,4 52,46 4,46" fill="none" stroke="#D97706" stroke-width="2" class="group-hover:fill-[#D97706]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="28" y="37" text-anchor="middle" fill="#D97706" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">S</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Soren</h3>
              <p class="text-[#D97706] text-xs font-semibold">Head of Research</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            The firm's intellectual foundation. Deep industry research, technology landscape monitoring, and the proprietary frameworks that give Nexus clients an analytical edge.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Industry analysis &middot; Tech trends &middot; Frameworks</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Petra -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#E11D48]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <polygon points="28,4 53,22 43,50 13,50 3,22" fill="none" stroke="#E11D48" stroke-width="2" class="group-hover:fill-[#E11D48]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="28" y="34" text-anchor="middle" fill="#E11D48" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">P</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Petra</h3>
              <p class="text-[#E11D48] text-xs font-semibold">Lead Engagement Manager</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Runs every client engagement from kickoff to final deliverable. Organized to the point of artistry — nothing falls through the cracks. Warm, professional, and relentlessly reliable.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Engagement execution &middot; Client management &middot; Coordination</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quinn -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#059669]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <polygon points="22,4 34,4 48,14 48,28 48,42 34,52 22,52 8,42 8,28 8,14" fill="none" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="2" class="group-hover:fill-[#059669]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="28" y="33" text-anchor="middle" fill="#059669" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">Q</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Quinn</h3>
              <p class="text-[#059669] text-xs font-semibold">Lead Analyst</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Makes the numbers defensible. Financial models, benchmarking, ROI analyses — every quantitative claim Nexus puts in front of a client traces back to Quinn's validated work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Financial modeling &middot; Benchmarking &middot; Data analysis</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Nova -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#7C3AED]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <path d="M28,2 L32,20 L50,16 L36,28 L50,40 L32,36 L28,54 L24,36 L6,40 L20,28 L6,16 L24,20 Z" fill="none" stroke="#7C3AED" stroke-width="1.8" class="group-hover:fill-[#7C3AED]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="28" y="33" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7C3AED" font-size="12" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">N</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Nova</h3>
              <p class="text-[#7C3AED] text-xs font-semibold">Brand & Content Lead</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            The voice of Nexus. Every whitepaper, case study, and client presentation — if it carries the Nexus name, Nova shaped it. Creative with strategic discipline.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Brand identity &middot; Thought leadership &middot; Content strategy</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cipher -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#374151]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <rect x="8" y="8" width="40" height="40" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="2" class="group-hover:fill-[#374151]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <text x="28" y="34" text-anchor="middle" fill="#374151" font-size="18" font-weight="300" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">&lt;/&gt;</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Cipher</h3>
              <p class="text-[#374151] text-xs font-semibold">Web & Digital Infrastructure</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Builds and maintains the firm's digital presence. Performance-obsessed and conversion-minded. Cipher treats the website as a product — not a brochure.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Web architecture &middot; Frontend &middot; Analytics</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Echo -->
        <div class="group bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#F97316]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 56 56" class="w-14 h-14">
                <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="8" fill="none" stroke="#F97316" stroke-width="2" class="group-hover:fill-[#F97316]/10 transition-all duration-300"/>
                <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="16" fill="none" stroke="#F97316" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.6"/>
                <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="24" fill="none" stroke="#F97316" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
                <text x="28" y="33" text-anchor="middle" fill="#F97316" font-size="10" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter, sans-serif">E</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy">Echo</h3>
              <p class="text-[#F97316] text-xs font-semibold">Social Media & Community</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Extends Nexus into the conversations that matter. Sharp, platform-native content for LinkedIn and beyond — designed to stop scrolling and provoke thinking.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-silver font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Social strategy &middot; Content creation &middot; Community</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Collaborate -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-pure-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Collaboration Model</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">How We Collaborate</h2>
        <p class="text-slate text-lg">Nexus operates as a network, not a hierarchy. While reporting lines establish accountability, work flows across roles on every engagement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Pair 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#3730A3]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#3730A3]">V</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#2563EB]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#2563EB]">K</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Veda + Kael</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Align strategy with delivery feasibility. Every recommendation is stress-tested against operational reality.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pair 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#D97706]">S</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#059669]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#059669]">Q</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Soren + Quinn</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Pair qualitative research with quantitative analysis. Insights backed by numbers, numbers informed by context.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pair 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#E11D48]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#E11D48]">P</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#059669]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#059669]">Q</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Petra + Quinn</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Integrate analysis into cohesive deliverables. Every engagement is structured and every number has a home.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pair 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#7C3AED]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#7C3AED]">N</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#D97706]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#D97706]">S</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Nova + Soren</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Turn research into compelling thought leadership. Intellectual depth meets audience-ready clarity.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pair 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-silver-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#2563EB]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#2563EB]">K</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-pure-white bg-[#7C3AED]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#7C3AED]">N</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy">Kael + Nova</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Co-own the final quality gate on every client deliverable. Nothing ships that would not hold up in a boardroom.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Result -->
        <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center">
          <div>
            <p class="text-teal-light text-sm font-semibold mb-2">The Result</p>
            <p class="text-pure-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Faster work, better work, and zero knowledge gaps between team members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Band -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pure-white mb-4">This team is ready to work on your challenge.</h2>
      <p class="text-silver text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Start with a Readiness Assessment. Six weeks. A clear, quantified picture of where you stand and where the value is.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-teal text-pure-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-light transition-colors text-lg">
        Book a Readiness Assessment
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
